# {r}
library(DT)
library(vegawidget)

# {r}
mydata <- palmerpenguins::penguins

# 
x_val <- "bill_length_mm"
y_val <- "bill_depth_mm"
group <- "species"

# {r}
# Vega-Lite spec
spec_mychart <-
  list(
    `$schema` = vega_schema(),
    data = list(name = "source"), # 
    mark = "point",
    encoding = list(
      x = list(field = x_val, type = "quantitative"),
      y = list(field = y_val, type = "quantitative"),
      color = list(field = group, type = "nominal")
    )
  ) |> 
  as_vegaspec()

# 
handler_data <-
  vw_handler_data("value")

# vegawidget
mychart <-
  vegawidget(spec_mychart, elementId = "my-chart") |> 
  vw_add_data_listener("source", handler_data)

# {r}
mytable <- 
  datatable(
    data = mydata,  # ) mydatadatatable
    filter = "top", # 
    elementId = "my-table"
  ) 

// {js}
$(document).ready(function(){ // dom
  let table = $('#my-table table'); // datatableID
  
  function data_update() {
    // JSON
    var data = table.DataTable().rows( {search: 'applied'} ).data().toArray(); // 
    var headers = table.dataTable().dataTableSettings[0].aoColumns; // 
    var JSONdata = [];
    
    for (var i = 0; i < data.length; i++) {
      var d = {};
      for (var j = 0; j < headers.length; j++) {
        var header = headers[j].sTitle;
        d[header] = data[i][j];
      }
      JSONdata.push(d);
    }
    
    // 
    Vegawidget.findViewPromise('#my-chart').then(function(view) {
      // 
      var changeSet = vega.changeset() 
                          .remove(vega.truthy)
                          .insert(JSONdata);
      // 
      view.change("source", changeSet).run();
    });
  }
  // 
  table.on("draw.dt", data_update);
  // 
  data_update();
});

mytable

mychart
